high_descs: Turn right go across the hall to the sink across from the sofa.
Pick up the ladle in the sink.
Turn right then turn left toward the hall, go across to the cabinet, and turn right to the nightstand.
Place the ladle in the tall cabinet on the right of the nightstand.
Go across to the bed to the left of the nightstand.
Pick up the ladle on the bed.
Go across the room to the tall cabinet.
Place the ladle in the tall cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place two ladles in a tall cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and go through the hallway, then take the first left into the kitchen area, going towards the sink.
Pick up the ladle from inside the sink.
Exit the kitchen area and turn left and straight into the bedroom, approaching the cabinet on the right in the corner.
Place the ladle inside the cabinet.
Turn towards the bed.
Pick up the ladle from the bed.
Return to the cabinet.
Place the ladle inside the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place two ladles inside a bedroom cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right. At the end of the wall, turn left. Reach the sink, turn right.
Grab the ladle.
Turn on the right. At the end of the wall go straight ahead. When you enter continue after the shelf and turn right. You arrive in front of the cabinet.
Turn right to the cabinet. Turn right, continue until you reach the wall.
Turn right. Grab the spoon from the bed.
Turn right. Take the ladle.
Turn right. Take the spoon from the cabinet.
Turn right. At the end of the bed, turn left. Reach the bedside table. Open the cabinet, place the ladle. Close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Find two ladles. Place them inside the cabinet.
